metadata.name: NURSES
metadata.description:
This is my first NFT on FND and collaboration with my two good friends - animations by @PatrickLawler & music composition by David Palmer. 

I'm also including a signed AP print with this purchase - 18x24 inches on cold-pressed archival paper ($550), signed by artist, embellished/hand-printed in Los Angeles. 

The original painting is called "Inoculation Breakthrough" from my series dedicated to female inventors in 2019. 

Dimensions: 1728 × 2160
